reviewText: This special is just bad.  I was very surprised because I like Foxx and looked forward to seeing Straight.  But time after time he went for the cheap joke.  That is fine if it is funny but this just wasn't. The standup material was dated and not even a little bit intelligent. Lowbrow, predictable and full of cliche`s.  Sorry-but don't waste your money.  I agree with the reviewer who said it took him 45 min. to laugh.  I don't even think I laughed then.  (How many times can you do the "Wanda" face?)
Jamie fox is so funny and talented. I love this dvd. He is one of the best.

I really enjoy Jamie Foxx's movies and stand-up but the material that is on this one is a lot of what the other two dvds consist of. If you want to see some laugh until you cry or your stomach aches comedy then order his other two dvds.
